query:
SELECT 
  p.apiId,
  a.name as apiName,
  a.priority,
  p.ourPrice,
  s.name as serviceName
FROM prices p
LEFT JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
LEFT JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
WHERE s.name LIKE '%WhatsApp%'
ORDER BY a.priority ASC
LIMIT 10
